In ml.linux.dev.kernel, you wrote:
>every now en then, I have the keyboard repeat rate and delay which
>seem to reset to the default BIOS speed of about 6 chars a second
>and 1 sec delay.
> [...]
>has anybody else seen this ? could this be a defect of my keyboard ?
It might be a stupid question, but since you didn't mention it,
did you try kbdrate(8) ?
"kbdrate -r 30" fixes this behaviour for me.
